These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: water, mirinda, lemonade, milk, cola, iced-tea, hot-chocolate
There are 7 different nationalities: indian, russian, turkish, japanese, colombian, american, argentine
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: snowboarding, water-polo, lacrosse, tennis, cycling, handball, soccer
The people use 7 different means of transport: snowmobile, trike, bus, boat, skateboard, motorbike, tram
 1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is cycling is the japanese##1
 3. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 4. the russian is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 5. the indian is on the right of the argentine##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 7. the person driving the tram is on the right of the colombian##1
 8. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the tram and the american##2
 9. the colombian is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
10. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person drinking cola##1
12. the person drinking cola is the person driving the snowmobile##1
13. the person drinking water is on the left of the turkish##1
14. the american is the person driving the bus##1
15. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the argentine##1
16. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
17. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the turkish##1
18. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the colombian##1
19. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | mirinda  | iced-tea        | cola | lemonade      | milk     | water      | hot-chocolate     |
| Nationality   | russian | japanese         | argentine   | indian | american    | colombian | turkish |
| Sport         | lacrosse | cycling | snowboarding | water-polo | soccer  | handball  | tennis    |
| Transport     | skateboard  | motorbike         | snowmobile     | trike    | bus | boat     | tram     |

