 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 7. the person eating peach is the person drinking juice##1
 8. the fan of techno is the person driving the bus##1
 9. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
10. the fan of hip-hop is between the fan of punk and the person eating grapes##2
11. the fan of jazz is the person eating corn##1
12. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
13. the fan of gospel is between the person eating grapes and the fan of r&b##2
14. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
15. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the van##1
16. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
17. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
18. the person eating vanrot is on the left of the person eating lime##1
19. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
20. the person eating lime is between the person driving the subway and the person eating vanrot##2

